{
  "__meta__": {
    "title":        "\"For Example\"",
    "subtitle":     "The Exemplary Journey."
  },

  "__main__": {
    "_": {
      "context": [
        "You stand at the foot of the cathedral, Exempli Gratia.",
        "The double-doors' stare pierces through you."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Enter the cathedral.",
          "follow_up": "You enter.",

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do not.",

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "leave-immediately-confirm"
        },
        {
          "text":      "(You must enter.)",
          "follow_up": "(And you do.)",

          "show_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "leave-immediately-confirm": {
      "context": [
        "Are you sure?",
        "You just got here..."
      ],

      "choices": [
        {
          "text":      "Leave.",
          "follow_up": "You leave.",

          "next": "ENDING-leave_immediately"
        },
        {
          "text":      "Stay.",
          "follow_up": "You stay.",

          "next": "_"
        }
      ]
    },

    "main_hall-start": {
      "context": [
        "You are in the main hall. The ceilings dizzy you.",
        "You feel at home, in spite of yourself."
      ],

      "choices": [
        { "text": "Let it wash over you.", "next": "extraction-0" },
        {
          "text":      "Leave.",
          "follow_up": "Behind you, a rhythmic thumping.",

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-0"
          },

          "next": "_"
        },
        {
          "text": "Try to leave.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You freeze. You can't.",
            "",
            "There is something you lost.",
            "(And something you gained.)"
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-0",
          "hide_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-1"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-0": {
      "context": [
        "You look deeply into the architecture, seeing yourself in the murals and supporting beams.",
        "It brings you great fear not knowing what you will find - should you proceed."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Continue.", "next": "extraction-1" },
        {
          "text": "Stop, while you can.",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Can you?)"
          ],

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "on_select": {
            "set": [ "resisted-0" ]
          },

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-1": {
      "context": [
        "You fall to your knees. Your vision blackens.",
        "There is a stinging wetness on your face.",
        "You feel a hot vapor engulfing you."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text":      "Do nothing.",
          "follow_up": "...",

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Have you no will?)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Indeed you have none.)",
            "",
            "Nothing happened."
          ],

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Your will could be stronger.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(But it was starved.)",
            "",
            "Nothing seemed to happen."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-0",
          "hide_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-1"
          },

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Your will is strong.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Perhaps strong enough.)",
            "",
            "Nothing seemed to happen."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-2"
          },

          "next": "extraction-last"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-last": {
      "context": [
        "And you go numb.",
        "",
        "It deteriorates - what remained of your sense of self.",
        "Although, you feel as though you must allow it to happen.",
        "",
        "You must submit.",
        "You must not have will."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-1", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        {
          "text": "(Resist.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "You open your eyes. The incessant spinning lets up.",
            "",
            "You peer into the reflective stained-glass, and see yourself.",
            "You find your face covered in a silver, opaque substance.",
            "You remember its sting.",
            "",
            "Your judgement now unclouded, you see that all else remains changed."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-1",

          "next": "main_hall"
        },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" }
      ]
    },

    "main_hall": {
      "context": [
        "That dim, orange twilight which once lit the room has now faded.",
        "The hall is still."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Look around.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You look.",
            "",
            "To your left, a marble statue of a woman.",
            "You make out a faint engraving at the base.",
            "",
            "Directly in front, a sea of wooden benches.",
            "It parts in the center, and leads to the sanctuary.",
            "A golden book lies upon its altar.",
            "",
            "To your right, the haunting stained-glass window.",
            "The depiction focuses on an individual gripping a torch.",
            "You perceive an unkind glow from the person.",
            "It betrays the setting sun."
          ],

          "hide_if": "looked_around",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "looked_around"
          },

          "next": "main_hall"
        },
        {
          "text": "Investigate the woman of marble.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You turn left and approach the statue.",
            "As you move, her gaze follows."
          ],

          "show_if": "looked_around",
          "hide_if": "",

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        },
        {
          "text": "Approach the altar.",

          "follow_up": "(I didn't do this yet)",

          "show_if": "looked_around",
          "hide_if": "",

          "next": "main_hall"
        },
        {
          "text": "Investigate the stained glass's glow.",

          "follow_up": "(I didn't do this yet)",

          "show_if": "looked_around",
          "hide_if": "",

          "next": "main_hall"
        }
      ]
    },

    "main_hall-statue": {
      "context": [
        "You stand at the foot of the marble statue.",
        "She towers above you."
      ],

      "choices": [
        { "text": "Go back.", "next": "main_hall" },
        {
          "text": "Read the engraving.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You lower your gaze to her pedestal.",
            "It reads:",
            "",
            "| \"Cogito, ergo sum\"",
            "| A lie sold as truth",
            "|",
            "| Our claim to our worth",
            "| Functions as its proof"
          ],

          "on_select": {
            "set": "statue-read_engraving"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        },
        {
          "text": "Admire the woman.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You peer up into her expressionless eyes.",
            "And you find nothing.",
            "",
            "There isn't a judgement that comes to your mind, nor hers.",
            "She showed you something."
          ],

          "on_select": {
            "set": "statue-admired"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"What did you show me?\"",
          "follow_up": [
            "(No response.)"
          ],

          "show_if": "statue-admired",
          "hide_if": "statue-ask-0",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "statue-ask-0"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Please, answer me.\"",
          "follow_up": [
            "(No response.)"
          ],

          "show_if": "statue-ask-0",
          "hide_if": "statue-ask-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "statue-ask-1"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"What am I missing?\"",
          "follow_up": [
            "(No response.)"
          ],

          "show_if": "statue-ask-1",

          "next": "main_hall-statue"
        }
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-leave_immediately": {
      "context": [
        "You don't look back.",
        "",
        "(You got the ending of a coward.)"
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-extracted": {
      "context": [
        "Of your life, you now infer that all but this one moment-",
        "",
        "This moment is all that matters now.",
        "         It is all.",
        "         It is all that matters.",
        "                   That matters.",
        "",
        "All that was before is now beneath you.",
        "                           Beneath you.",
        "",
        "You are not here, and yet you are.",
        "                          You are.",
        "You are not               you.",
        "",
        "(You failed to avoid extraction.)"
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-extraction_failed": {
      "context": [
        "You cannot keep your eyes closed.",
        "You                        lose.",
        "",
        "Your fear is too strong.",
        "Your ego would not die.",
        "You      would not die.",
        "",
        "You recall the wounds that which you hid from the world.",
        "           The wounds.",
        "And you realize that they are precisely what kept you here.",
        "           The wounds     are            from the world.",
        "And                   they           hid",
        "                                 you from     you.",
        "    You                   are                         here.",
        "",
        "(You narrowly avoided extraction.)"
      ]
    }
  }
}